SYNOPSIS

       In configuration:
    
       [YAML]
       select = **/*.yaml
       Indent = 4

DESCRIPTION

    Uses YAML to format YAML files. Has the same defaults as YAML.pm

CONFIGURATION

    The following configuration options can be set. See YAML for a full
    description of each option.

    AnchorPrefix

    CompressSeries

    DumpCode

    Indent

    QuoteNumericStrings

    SortKeys

    Stringify

    UseAliases

    UseBlock

    UseCode

    UseFold

    UseHeader

    UseVersion

SEE ALSO

    Code::TidyAll, YAML

